    <h1>About ToolCalcs</h1>

    <p>ToolCalcs is a free online resource providing accurate, easy-to-use calculators for everyday needs. Whether you are planning your finances, tracking your health goals, or solving math problems, our tools are designed to give you quick, reliable results.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We believe everyone should have access to accurate calculation tools without complicated interfaces, paywalls, or excessive advertising. Our calculators are built to be simple, fast, and mobile-friendly.</p>

    <h2>What We Offer</h2>
    <p>ToolCalcs provides <strong>40 interactive calculators</strong> across 6 categories, plus <strong>over 500 quick-answer pages</strong> for specific conversions, percentages, countdowns, and currency exchanges.</p>

    <h3>Interactive Calculators</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong><a href="/financial-calculators/">Financial Calculators:</a></strong> Compound interest, loan amortization, mortgage, take-home pay, retirement savings, auto loan, paycheck, inflation, and savings goal tools.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="/health-calculators/">Health Calculators:</a></strong> BMI, TDEE, calorie, body fat, ideal weight, pregnancy due date, pace, ovulation, and sleep calculators.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="/math-calculators/">Math Calculators:</a></strong> Percentage, fraction, GPA, random number, standard deviation, area, and probability tools.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="/date-time-calculators/">Date & Time Calculators:</a></strong> Age calculator, date difference, days-until countdown, and time zone converter.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="/conversion-calculators/">Conversion Calculators:</a></strong> Unit converter and currency converter for length, weight, temperature, volume, and world currencies.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="/everyday-calculators/">Everyday Calculators:</a></strong> Tip, discount, hours, square footage, gas cost, electricity cost, and word counter tools.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Quick Answer Pages</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong><a href="/convert/">Unit Conversions:</a></strong> 90+ specific conversion pages like <a href="/convert/inches-to-centimeters/">inches to centimeters</a> and <a href="/convert/pounds-to-kilograms/">pounds to kilograms</a>.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="/percentage/">Percentages:</a></strong> 285 quick-answer pages like <a href="/percentage/20-percent-of-100/">what is 20% of 100</a>.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="/how-many/">How Many?:</a></strong> 31 common measurement questions like <a href="/how-many/cups-in-a-gallon/">how many cups in a gallon</a>.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="/days-until/">Countdowns:</a></strong> 39 countdown pages for holidays and events like <a href="/days-until/christmas/">days until Christmas</a>.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="/currency/">Currency Exchange:</a></strong> 54 currency pair pages like <a href="/currency/usd-to-eur/">USD to EUR</a> with conversion tables.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Accuracy & Privacy</h2>
    <p>All calculations are performed directly in your browser. We do not send your data to any server. Your numbers stay on your device.</p>
    <p>Our calculators use industry-standard formulas and are regularly reviewed for accuracy. However, they are for informational purposes only and should not replace professional financial, medical, or legal advice.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Have a question, suggestion, or found a bug? We would love to hear from you. Visit our <a href="/contact/">contact page</a> to get in touch.</p>
